custom-block.comment: run your code as each point in a 2D grid

custom-block.s: grid %s by %s by %s with step size %s %cs

custom-block.comment: place a cuboid or tube along your path as you move
run your code at each point on a circle
easily switch between drawing lines or extrusions
go to points on the surface of a sphere

scripts.comment: To use these blocks in your own projects, use the "export blocks" item in the file menu to save them. then you can import them into your own project.

block-definition.s: grid %'x steps' by %'y steps' with step size %'step' %'blocks'
grid %'x steps' by %'y steps' by %'z steps' with step size %'step' %'blocks'
